<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 text-center mb-5">
      <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary">About Notify</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row align-items-center">
    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7">
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="lead">
          Welcome to <strong>NOTIFY</strong>, your personal, clutter-free space for capturing thoughts, reminders, and plans.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Notify is a free, lightweight web app built using Node.js, EJS, and MongoDB, designed to simplify note-taking while keeping your data secure and accessible only to you. Whether you're managing daily to-dos, saving ideas on the go, or creating a space for personal journaling, Notify gives you a clean and focused environment to stay on track.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Unlike complex productivity tools overloaded with features, Notify is intentionally simple, fast to load, easy to use, and built for anyone who wants their notes organized without the noise.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          So whether you're a student, developer, creator, or just someone who likes keeping life in order, Notify is made to be your quiet digital companion.
        </p>
        
        <blockquote class="blockquote text-center my-6 py-3 bg-light rounded">
          <p class="mb-0 fst-italic">"Think it. Write it. Store it. Find it later — that's the Notify way."</p>
          <span class="fs-7"></span>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Creator Photo and Info Section -->
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-5 text-center">
      <div class="creator-section">
        <!-- Bigger Circular Photo -->
        <div class="creator-photo mb-4">
